<p>SecurityStatus message contains status of a <a href="glossary/instrument">instrument</a>. Information like trading status, corporate actions or financial status of a company may be reported.</p>

<p>SecurityStatus messages are emitted via PUB socket as a result of subscription defined in a <a href="msgtypes/SecurityStatusRequest">SecurityStatusRequest</a> message</p>

